IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. PROCDEMO.
PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    MOVE 1 TO WS-A WS-B.
    MOVE CORRESPONDING WS-GROUP TO WS-OUT.
    MOVE WS-TABLE(WS-A) TO WS-B.
    MOVE WS-NAME OF WS-REC TO WS-OUT.
    MOVE WS-FIELD(1:3) TO WS-OUT.
    DISPLAY "Count:" WS-A UPON CONSOLE.
    DISPLAY WS-B WITH NO ADVANCING.
    ACCEPT WS-A FROM DATE.
    MOVE 1 TO WS-A DISPLAY WS-A.
    GO TO END-PARA.
    CONTINUE.
    STOP RUN.
